### For Loop

func main(){

  sum:= 0
  for i:= 0; i<10; i++ {
    sum+= i
  }
  fmt.Println(sum)
}

### For loop without init and increment operator is a while loop

  for ; sum<1000 ; {
  sum+=sum
  }
  
  ///// Same as
  
  for sum<1000 {
  sum+=sum
  }

### Forever loop

  for {
  ::
  }
  
-------------------------------

